data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a spacious corner lot within the coveted North Rock Creek School District. Boasting a generous 1.32-acre expanse, this property offers the perfect blend of modern upgrades and serene outdoor living.

Step into the heart of the home, where the beautifully renovated kitchen (completed in 2020) stands as a testament to both style and functionality. With its sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage, this kitchen is a chef's dream. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living area, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining.

Both bathrooms have undergone tasteful renovations. The thoughtful upgrades extend outdoors, with an extended patio (2019) providing a delightful setting for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment.

Key updates have been thoughtfully executed, including a new roof (2023), ensuring peace of mind for years to come. The front storm door (replaced in 2022) and new ceiling fans throughout enhance both aesthetics and energy efficiency. The home's systems have also been cared for, with the hot water tank and pressure tank replaced in 2020, offering modern convenience.

Embrace the Oklahoma landscape on this expansive lot, complete with a chain link fence for added security and a sense of privacy. An underground storm shelter provides reassurance during inclement weather, while the 2-car garage offers ample storage and convenience.

Located mere minutes from downtown Shawnee, you'll enjoy easy access to a plethora of amenities, restaurants, and entertainment options. Say goodbye to HOA restrictions, as this property offers the freedom to personalize your space to your heart's content.

With 1,541 square feet, this home is a true gem within North Rock Creek School District. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property yours and experience the perfect blend of modern living and natural serenity.
